column24: Table 4. Summary of prey items identiﬁed in harbor seal (Phoca vitulina) scats collected from Tugidak Island Alaska from 2001 to 2009. The scenario provided for each of these species denotes whether the relative importance of each species was estimated to be higher by ssFO than BR (Scenario 1)\ higher according to BR than ssFO (Scenario 2)\ or if neither estimation method dominated (Scenario 3). Examples of each scenario are portrayed in Fig. 2.
